    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Magtong</i> is a frantic, physics-based sports game where magnetic forces collide in a battle of speed, strategy, and style. Slam, repel, and attract your way to victory in matches that are easy to pick up but hard to master.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you're teaming up or flying solo, locally or online, <i>Magtong</i> delivers fast-paced action and unpredictable fun for all skill levels.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Magnetic airhockey with unique physics</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Local and Online Multiplayer</strong> - even mixed play is supported!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Quick, bite-sized rounds</strong> perfect for spontaneous competitions with friends</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Pull and Push based on ball polarity (Opposites attract!)</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044580/extras/53e29d399214c3917fb2d62e824c502f.poster.avif?t=1767034696\" width=750 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044580/extras/53e29d399214c3917fb2d62e824c502f.webm?t=1767034696\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044580/extras/53e29d399214c3917fb2d62e824c502f.mp4?t=1767034696\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Switch the polarity of the puck to get one up on your opponent!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044580/extras/d4e2e71ae99ed65212b85239b2fb61f0.poster.avif?t=1767034696\" width=750 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044580/extras/d4e2e71ae99ed65212b85239b2fb61f0.webm?t=1767034696\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044580/extras/d4e2e71ae99ed65212b85239b2fb61f0.mp4?t=1767034696\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Shoot faster shots with the pulse ability</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044580/extras/d6e1f1795d5577e429746af09a80f9fc.poster.avif?t=1767034696\" width=750 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044580/extras/d6e1f1795d5577e429746af09a80f9fc.webm?t=1767034696\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044580/extras/d6e1f1795d5577e429746af09a80f9fc.mp4?t=1767034696\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
